<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT50">
<l>kūṟṟamuñ cārā koṭuviṉaiyuñ cārātī</l>
<l>māṟṟamuñ cārā vakaiyaṟintē ṉāṟṟaṅ</l>
<l>karaikkiṭakkuṅ kaṇṇaṉ kaṭalkiṭakkumāya</l>
<l>ṉuraikkiṭakku muḷḷat teṉakku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have learnt the means of not [having] death, or the cruel karman,</l>
<l rend="indent">or evil diversity approach.</l>
<l>The words of Kṛṣṇa who reclines on the riverbank,</l>
<l>The Dark One who reclines on the ocean</l>
<l rend="indent">rest in my heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
